_official" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nanashinku</a> ”的选秀活动将持续至8月31日（周六）。</p><p>申请对象为“18岁以上女性”、“能够连续进行直播活动的人”、“不分国籍（能用日语交流的人）”。</p><p><a href="https://774-audition.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>了解试镜详情。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000037.000071134.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">774株式会社新闻稿</a></p><h2>Hololive x Dodekamin 合作活动实施</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/d58b95dffd83b350dc479e019a82865c-kix.8pp8a8tqvgtj-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/d58b95dffd83b350dc479e019a82865c-kix.8pp8a8tqvgtj-1024x337.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/d58b95dffd83b350dc479e019a82865c-kix.8pp8a8tqvgtj-1024x337.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/d58b95dffd83b350dc479e019a82865c-kix.8pp8a8tqvgtj-300x99.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/d58b95dffd83b350dc479e019a82865c-kix.8pp8a8tqvgtj-768x253.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/d58b95dffd83b350dc479e019a82865c-kix.8pp8a8tqvgtj-1536x505.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/d58b95dffd83b350dc479e019a82865c-kix.8pp8a8tqvgtj-jpg.webp 1578w" width="1024" height="337" /></a></p><p> Hololive与Dodekamin的合作活动将于7月30日（周二）起限时举办。</p><p>通过访问目标产品上附带的活动贴纸并积累积分，您可以申请通过抽奖赢得数字内容、亚克力支架等的活动。</p><p> <a href="https://www.asahiinryo.co.jp/entertainment/campaign/dodecamin/hololive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>了解活动详细信息。</p><p> © 2016 COVER 公司</p><p>（参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000769.000039153.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">朝日软饮料新闻稿</a></p><h2>Nijisanji的第一张模拟唱片和CD将同时发行</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/d58b95dffd83b350dc479e019a82865c-kix.eod5mnew0t1t-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/d58b95dffd8